## Installation
### 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/sithu-devhub/blog-management-system.git

### 2. Navigate to the project folder
cd blog-management-system

### 3. Install dependencies
npm install

### 4. Run the application
npm start

---

## Application URLs
Main application
http://localhost:3000/

Test routes
404 error test
http://localhost:3000/test

500 error test
http://localhost:3000/error-test

